To assay free radical scavenging activity22, 50 µl of the prepared extract with respect to the does explained above was added to 950 µl of 6 × 10−5 mol. l−1 (free radical, 95%) in methanol. The solution was precisely shocked and left at room temperature for 15 min. The absorption was then measured at 517 nm and the inhibition percentage of the DPPH radical was appraised as follows:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
